The three pigs moved out of their old house and started building their own house. 
Pig1 built his out of hay, pig2 built his out of sticks, the third built his out of brick.
Pig3's house took the most time and work.
One day the big bad Wolf wanted to eat the pigs.
He went to Pig1's house and blew his house away. 
Pig1 ran to Pig2's house. 
The wolf blew Pig2's house away.
Then the two pig went to Pig3's house. 
The wolf could not blow his houe away nomatter how hard he tried.
The wolf ran away.